OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud and any fog
OL,6,Flifting in the east, then warm hazy
OL,7,Fsunshine England and Wales. However,
OL,8,Fcloudier with showers Scotland and
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, and isolated showers
OL,10,Felsewhere later in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy across Scotland with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain, heavy at times in the
OL,14,Fnorth. Elsewhere, mostly dry though
OL,15,Fthe odd shower still possible with
OL,16,Fmist and fog patches in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
