OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunny in the south on Monday.
OL,6,FCloudier to the north with rain or
OL,7,Fshowers. These eventually sinking
OL,8,Fsouthwards into central England,
OL,9,Fturning heavy and possibly thundery
OL,10,Flater in the day.
